{
  "text": "According to [CITATION_1] the key element of social revolution and transformation in educational institutes is nothing less than equipping students with general ICT knowledge and skills. This includes technical exposure to inspire lifelong learning; making best and appropriate use of social software technologies for conceptualization, representation, communication; individual development and professional competence.",
